predictions.article: Trade war escalates as retaliatory tariffs hit struggling farm economy
predictions.prediction: The imposition of tariffs by the U.S. on China, Canada, and Mexico, followed by retaliatory tariffs, will lead to a decrease in U.S. agricultural exports to these countries by at least 10% within the next month.
